# ============================================
# NavGate Frontend Environment Configuration
# 前端环境配置
# ============================================
#
# 这个文件是示例，复制为 .env.local 并填入你的实际值
# This is an example file. Copy to .env.local and fill in your values
#
# cp .env.local.example .env.local
#
# ⚠️ 重要：.env.local 不会被提交到 Git（已在 .gitignore 中）
# ⚠️ Important: .env.local will not be committed to Git (in .gitignore)
#

# ============================================
# 模式 1: localStorage 模式（默认）
# Mode 1: localStorage Mode (Default)
# ============================================
# 
# 无需配置，直接使用
# No configuration needed, works out of the box
#
VITE_DEPLOY_MODE=github-pages

# ============================================
# 模式 2: GitHub Gist 模式（推荐）⭐
# Mode 2: GitHub Gist Mode (Recommended) ⭐
# ============================================
#
# 跨设备同步 / Cross-device sync
# 版本历史 / Version history
# 免费可靠 / Free and reliable
#
# 取消注释以下行并填入你的值：
# Uncomment the lines below and fill in your values:
#
# VITE_DEPLOY_MODE=gist
# VITE_GIST_ID=abc123def456...
# VITE_GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
#
# 获取这些值 / Get these values:
# 1. GitHub Token: https://github.com/settings/tokens (需要 gist 权限 / need gist scope)
# 2. Gist ID: https://gist.github.com/ (创建 Gist 后从 URL 获取 / get from URL after creating Gist)
#
# 详细步骤 / Detailed steps:
# - QUICK_START.md
# - ENV_CONFIG_GUIDE.md

# ============================================
# 模式 3: 后端模式
# Mode 3: Backend Mode
# ============================================
#
# 需要运行后端服务器 / Requires backend server
#
# 取消注释以下行：
# Uncomment the lines below:
#
# VITE_DEPLOY_MODE=backend
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:3000
#
# 详细步骤 / Detailed steps:
# - DEPLOYMENT_MODES.md
# - ENV_SETUP.md
